title: Vegans can be idiots, too. Activism is fake, stupidity is real.
description: Vegans can also be malicious, dishonest, and even violent, in case you hadn't noticed, lately.  Bronze-age virtues, people: having a code of honor matters, treating people with dignity matters.  There's a big difference between telling someone they're stupid (directly, in private e-mails, or in a public debate) and defaming someone on the internet.
